@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Awareness";
    Layout = "_CounsellingPatient";
}
<br />
<br />
<section class="we-offer-area text-center bg-gray">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="">
                <div class="site-heading text-center">
                    <h2>Mental Health Awareness</h2>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row justify-content-center align-content-center">
                <p style="width:70%">
                    Mental health awareness is crucial for recognizing and addressing mental health issues early on. It involves understanding the importance of mental well-being, recognizing the signs and symptoms of mental health conditions, and knowing how to seek help.
                    <br />
                    <br />
                    Promoting mental health awareness helps reduce stigma, encourages people to talk about their mental health, and fosters a supportive community. By increasing awareness, we can create an environment where individuals feel comfortable seeking help and accessing the resources they need.
                    <br />
                    <br />
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <div class="site-heading text-center">
                    <h2>What is counseling?</h2>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row justify-content-center align-content-center">
                <p style="width:70%">
                    Counseling is a professional service that offers support, guidance, and therapy to individuals facing various life challenges. Counselors are trained to help you navigate emotional, psychological, and interpersonal issues.
                    <br />
                    <br />
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <div class="site-heading text-center">
                    <h2>Why is counseling important?</h2>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row justify-content-center align-content-center">
                <p style="width:70%">
                    Counseling is vital for mental health and well-being. It provides a safe space to express your feelings, explore your thoughts, and work through your problems with the help of a trained professional.
                    <br />
                    <br />
                    Regular counseling sessions can help you develop coping strategies, improve your relationships, and achieve personal growth. It's also a time to ask questions and get advice on managing stress, anxiety, depression, and other mental health issues.
                    <br />
                    <br />
                </p>
            </div>
            <br />
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <div class="site-heading text-center">
                    <h2>How often should I attend counseling sessions?</h2>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row justify-content-center align-content-center">
                <p style="width:70%">
                    The frequency of counseling sessions depends on your individual needs and circumstances. Generally, it is recommended to start with weekly sessions to build a strong therapeutic relationship and address immediate concerns. Over time, sessions may become bi-weekly or monthly as you make progress.
                    <br />
                    <ul>
                        <li>Weekly sessions for the initial phase of counseling</li>
                        <li>Bi-weekly sessions as you start to see improvement</li>
                        <li>Monthly check-ins for maintenance and ongoing support</li>
                    </ul>
                    Your counselor will work with you to determine the best schedule based on your specific situation.
                    <br />
                    <br />
                </p>
            </div>
            <br />
        </div>
        <p style="font-size:x-large">
            Book Your Counseling Session Today
            <br />
            <a asp-action="Appointment" asp-controller="Counselor" class="btn btn-primary"><i class="fa-solid fa-heart-circle-check"></i> Book an appointment</a>
        </p>
    </div>
</section>


